- HeaderConverter.java - uses `heading.getText()` which loses formatting (needs fixing too)
- Pattern: `Node node = paragraph.getFirstChild(); while (node != null) { ... node = node.getNext(); }`

PATTERNS:
- Simple node iteration: `getFirstChild()` / `getNext()` pattern used in HeaderConverter and ParagraphConverter
- Creating runs: `XWPFRun run = paragraph.createRun()` then `run.setText()`, `run.setBold(true)`

