   - Replace the simple StringBuilder text extraction with InlineTextConverter
   - Pass the XWPFParagraph to InlineTextConverter so it can create runs with formatting

3. Update HeaderConverter to use InlineTextConverter (headers can contain bold too)
   - Replace `heading.getText()` with InlineTextConverter

